plugin: manual
id: gnome-weather
flags: simple
_description:
 PURPOSE:
       Check that gnome-weather runs and works correctly
 STEPS:
      1. Run gnome-weather from the desktop icon. Does the icon look correct?
      2. Add a city and make sure the weather is correct. Test hourly and daily.
      3. Use the hamburger menu to switch between fahrenheit and celcius
      4. Make sure hamburger menu -> About brings up the About page

unit: test plan
id: gnome-weather-tp
name: gnome-weather test plan
include: gnome-weather
